til.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749564659,出现次数:1\r\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749564659 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\r\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"cc2deaae-6a54-4704-af86-fc33d176025a\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/product/2ZYFJ3GM2N\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to retrieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"275cb379-963b-4359-a2d1-e60c7d5aaa0a\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-10T14:19:55.142570185Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\r\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-1", "frontend-2", "frontend-0", "adservice-0"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-03"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-10T14:10:58Z to 2025-06-10T14:28:58Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 14:10:58+00:00 to 2025-06-10 14:28:58+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in request response time (rrt) observed during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt values escalate from 12057.08 to 36097.54, with P99 values rising from 13422.51 to 44518.44.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"High node CPU usage detected (node_cpu_usage_rate increment).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median ratio shift from 27 to 37% exceeded latency safety-growth gaps.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "日志数据已获取，与 UUID `7984364a-195` 相关的事件包括 31 条错误日志。我现在将根据日志内容扫描显著异常调用链，并识别关键故障模式。\n\n以下是分析总结: \n\n#### 数据主要发现\n1. **高频报错**：\n   - 错误关键词：\"failed to get ads: rpc error\" 和 \"context deadline exceeded\"。\n   - 报错组件：服务 `frontend` 大量请求无法获取广告，由 `adservice` 提供 RPC 服务。\n\n2. **异常模式**：\n   - 错误类型主要表现为 `DeadlineExceeded` 和 `context canceled`，表明存在 RPC 请求的等待超时问题。\n   - `adservice`中出现 Java 异常（例如 `InvocationTargetException` 和 Byteman 规则触发日志），表明服务内部可能存在处理瓶颈或规则注入失败。\n\n3. **可能的根因**：\n   - **adservice** 是主要公共服务，有多个前端组件抱怨它处理请求超时。\n   - Byteman规则可能干扰了正常的广告数据生成过程。\n\n#### 报告格式 (JSON输出)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context canceled\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Byteman Trigger\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务规则干扰或代理超时导致广告服务无法完成 RPC 请求。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志中出现 'DeadlineExceeded' 和 Byteman相关消息，表明 adservice 内部代理触发规则执行可能失败。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端频繁请求广告服务（adservice），导致超时积压。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志显示多个前端 pod 在同一时间大量超时 ‘context canceled’。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n上述分析提取了多个故障相关日志片段，后续需聚焦对 `adservice` 进行特别检查，以确认是否因带宽或规则执行过程故障。", "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是对 UUID 7984364a-195 相关的异常追踪数据分析结果：\n\n### 异常调用链发现和延迟分析\n\n以下是数据中发现的异常调用链，按照显著延迟和错误传播路径分析：\n\n1. **Frontend → AdService**\n   - **异常耗时**: 正常平均耗时约 5431 毫秒，异常期间平均耗时高达 499064 毫秒。\n   - **状态**: 多次出现 `context deadline exceeded` 错误。\n   - **瓶颈**: **Frontend 节点**对 **AdService** 的调用出现了极端延迟，是主要瓶颈。\n\n2. **Frontend → ProductCatalogService**\n   - **异常耗时**: 从正常的 9948 毫秒到异常的 9478 毫秒，并不显著。\n   - **状态**: 没有显著的错误。\n\n3. **CheckoutService → PaymentService**\n   - **异常耗时**: 正常平均耗时 13679 毫秒，异常期间平均耗时 84963 毫秒。\n   - **瓶颈**: **PaymentService** 可能是另一个延迟的根源。\n\n4. **CartService → Redis**\n   - **异常耗时**: 从正常的 1361 毫秒到异常的 12272 毫秒。\n   - **瓶颈**: 在 **Redis** 上有更长的响应时间。\n\n### 错误状态统计\n\n1. **AdService** 调用频繁出现 `context deadline exceeded` 错误，尤其通过 **Frontend** 的调用。\n2. **小网络错误**: `stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL` 发生较低频次。\n\n### 假设与验证\n\n以下是根据分析做出的几个假设：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"frontend->adservice\", \"context_deadline_exceeded\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常耗时和 deadline exceeded 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时约 5431 毫秒，异常期间耗时高达 499064 毫秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"CheckoutService 调用 PaymentService 期间显著延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 13679 毫秒，异常期间耗时 84963 毫秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"CartService 调用期间响应时间延长\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 1361 毫秒，异常期间耗时 12272 毫秒\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据数据，核心问题集中在 **AdService** 和 **PaymentService** 的延迟。AdService 的 `context deadline exceeded` 是主要的错误指示。建议深入检查这两个服务的处理时间和网络连接以定位根因并优化性能。"}
